Usage: cardano-cli to-verification [--byron-legacy-formats | --byron-formats]
                                   --secret FILEPATH --to FILEPATH

  Extract a verification key in its base64 form.

Available options:
  --byron-legacy-formats   Byron/cardano-sl formats and compatibility
  --byron-formats          Byron era formats and compatibility
  --secret FILEPATH        Signing key file to extract the verification part
                           from.
  --to FILEPATH            Non-existent file to write the verification key to.
  -h,--help                Show this help text
